    "content": "No, Dub does not have an API yet, but it is [planned for September 2023](https://github.com/steven-tey/dub/issues/73#issuecomment-1638409034).\n\nIf you would like to be notified when the API is available, please [sign up for the waitlist](https://tally.so/r/wdN50V).",
    "title": "Does Dub have an API?",
    "updatedAt": "2023-07-26",
    "summary": "Dub has an API that allows you to create, update, and delete links programmatically.",
