    "content": "First of all, thank you for upgrading to a paid plan on Dub!\n\nAs a 100% bootstrapped and [open-source](https://dub.sh/github) company, you support means the world to us and helps us continue\nto build and improve Dub.\n\n## Downloading your Dub invoice from Stripe\n\nSince we use [Stripe](https://stripe.com) to process payments, you can download your Dub invoice from Stripe by following the steps below:\n\n1. From your project dashboard (e.g. `app.dub.co/your-project`), click on the **Settings** tab.\n2. On the left sidebar, click on **Billing**.\n3. Click on the **Manage Subscription** button to go to your Stripe dashboard.\n\n<Image\n  alt=\"Billing section on Dub\"\n  src=\"https://d2vwwcvoksz7ty.cloudfront.net/help/manage-subscription.png\"\n  width={1331}\n  height={705}\n/>\n\n4. Scroll down to the **Invoice History** section.\n\n<Image\n  alt=\"Invoice history section on Stripe dashboard\"\n  src=\"https://d2vwwcvoksz7ty.cloudfront.net/help/invoice-history.png\"\n  width={1593}\n  height={1002}\n/>\n\n5. Here, you can access all your past invoices and download them as PDFs.",
    "title": "How can I download my Dub invoice?",
