    "content": "On Dub, you can easily invite your teammates to join your Dub project. This is useful if you want to collaborate with your team.\n\n## Sending an invite\n\nIf you haven't already, [create a project](what-is-a-project#how-to-create-a-project) on Dub.\n\nTo invite a teammate:\n\n1. Navigate to your project's Members Settings page. You can do that by clicking on the **Settings** link in the menu bar at the top of your project dashboard, and click on the **People** tab on the left sidebar.\n2. Click on the **Invite** button to open the Invite Teammate modal.\n3. Enter your teammate's email address and click on the **Send invite** button.\n\n<Image\n  alt=\"The Invite Teammate modal in Dub\"\n  src=\"https://d2vwwcvoksz7ty.cloudfront.net/help/invite-teammate-modal.png\"\n  width={1127}\n  height={730}\n/>\n\nYour teammate will receive an invitation to join your Dub project via email:\n\n<Image\n  alt=\"Email invitation to join a Dub project\"\n  src=\"https://d2vwwcvoksz7ty.cloudfront.net/help/project-invite-email.png\"\n  width={1072}\n  height={752}\n/>\n\n<Note variant=\"info\">\n  Invitations will be valid for 14 days – after which you will need to send a\n  new one.\n</Note>\n\n## Revoking / resending an invite\n\nIf you want to revoke / resend an invitation, you can do so by following these steps:\n\n1. Navigate to your project's Members Settings page.\n2. CLick on the **Invitations** tab.\n3. Click on the `⋮` button next to the invitation you want to revoke.\n4. Click on the **Remove** button to open the Remove Invitation modal.\n5. Click on the **Confirm remove** button to confirm.\n\n<Image\n  alt=\"The Remove Invitation modal in Dub\"\n  src=\"https://d2vwwcvoksz7ty.cloudfront.net/help/remove-invite-modal.png\"\n  width={1465}\n  height={855}\n/>\n\n## Removing a teammate\n\nIf a teammate no longer needs access to your project, you can remove them from your project.\n\n1. Navigate to your project's Members Settings page.\n2. Click on the `⋮` button next to the teammate you want to remove.\n3. Click on the **Remove** button to open the Remove Teammate modal.\n4. Click on the **Confirm remove** button to confirm.\n\n<Image\n  alt=\"The Remove Teammate modal in Dub\"\n  src=\"https://d2vwwcvoksz7ty.cloudfront.net/help/remove-teammate-modal.png\"\n  width={1322}\n  height={901}\n/>\n\n## How many teammates can I invite?\n\nDub has the most generous free plan in the industry. You can invite up to 2 teammates to your project (3 total users) on the free plan.\n\nNeed to invite more teammates? Upgrade to our [Pro plan](/pricing) for unlimited teammates.",
