    "content": "On Dub, a \"Project\" is a space that you can use to store all the short links for your website, app, or business.\n\nYou can think of a Dub project as a \"Team\" – you can [invite your teammates](how-to-invite-teammates) to join your project and manage the links together.\n\n## How to create a project\n\nTo create a project, go to the [Dub Dashboard](https://app.dub.co/) and click on the **Create project** button.\n\n<Image\n  alt=\"The project creation modal in Dub\"\n  src=\"https://d2vwwcvoksz7ty.cloudfront.net/help/create-project-modal.png\"\n  width={1315}\n  height={871}\n/>\n\nHere are the fields in the project creation modal:\n\n1. **Project Name**: This is the name of your project on Dub.\n2. **Project Slug**: This is your project's unique slug on Dub.\n3. **Shortlink Domain**: This is the domain that your short links will be hosted on. E.g. `yourbrand.com/link`.\n\nOnce you have filled in the fields, click on the **Create project** button to create your project.\n\n## Onboarding checklist\n\nAfter you have created your project, you will be redirected to the project dashboard. Here, you will see a checklist of things that you can do to get started with your project.\n\n<Image\n  alt=\"Onboarding checklist for a new project in Dub\"\n  src=\"https://d2vwwcvoksz7ty.cloudfront.net/help/onboarding-checklist.png\"\n  width={1529}\n  height={978}\n/>\n\n1. **Configure your custom domain**: You can [configure your custom domain](how-to-add-custom-domain) to use your own domain for your short links.\n2. **Create or import your links**: You can [create links](how-to-create-link) or [import existing ones](how-to-import-bitly-links) to your project.\n3. **Invite your teammates**: You can [invite your teammates](how-to-invite-teammates) to join your project and manage the links together.\n\n## How many domains can I add to a project?\n\nYou can [add as many domains](how-to-add-custom-domain) as you want to a project. If your project has multiple domains, you will be able to filter the links in the project by their respective domains.\n\n<Image\n  alt=\"Filtering links by domain in Dub\"\n  src=\"https://d2vwwcvoksz7ty.cloudfront.net/changelog/unlimited-domains.png\"\n  width={1607}\n  height={945}\n/>\n\n## Limits and Billing for Projects\n\nThere is no limit as to how many projects you can create on Dub – you can create as many projects as you want, and each project will be billed separately.",
